## App.vue Integration

`App.vue` renders based on `startupStore.phase`:
- `splash` ‚Üí `StartupSplash`
- `setup-*` ‚Üí `StartupLayout` wrapping the appropriate step component
- `select-character` ‚Üí `CharacterSelect`
- `loading` ‚Üí `StartupProgress`
- `ready` ‚Üí Main app (MenuBar + view components)

The main app initialization (coordinator polling, event listeners, auto-start watchers)
only runs when phase transitions to `ready`, via a watcher on `startup.phase`.

CDN game data loading is non-blocking ‚Äî it runs in the background and does not
gate the startup flow.
